description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Chukcha purrs with a rating of 77, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 154, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 2 for East, 8 for South, and Leverage for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30772-72861-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [154 Votes, Top 9% Rating]
